text: Nicola June McLean (born 18 September 1981) is a British model and reality television personality. Due to being a successful model, McLean appeared on multiple reality TV shows including I'm a Celebrity...Get Me Out of Here 2008 and also appeared Celebrity Big Brother twice, in 2012 and 2017. McLean is married to footballer Tom Williams and they have two sons. Her family is Scottish. == Sources == Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:British models Category:British television personalities
